mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "On the Record and Record Report", "Square Dance Datebook", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "Basic Movements-Introduction and Suggested Order of Teaching", "The Dancer's Walk-Thru", "Dialog for Callers", "Convention News", "Callers of the Month: Bob Augustin, Paul Clements, Herb Keys, Harold Parker, George Ruddock, Gary Shoemake, Harry Tucciarone, Jr. and Bruno Zeni", "Style Series: Do Si Do", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "SIO Workshop", "Handbook Supplement: The Basic Movements of Square Dancing", "Paging the Round Dancers: Fred and Gwen Manning", "Current Best Sellers", and "Experimental Lab: Cross Run".
